Package org.universAAL.lddi.knx.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IKnxDriverClient
    Applications using KNXDriver should implement this IF to get event messages from real Sensors (incoming) and to send events to Actuators (outgoing).
    IKnxNetwork  
    IKnxReceiveMessage
    Define receive methods for messages from knx bus.
    IKnxSendMessage
    Define send methods for messages to knx bus.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KnxDriver
    This abstract class is designed to help developing a knx driver.
